PRICE IMPROVEMENT No CDD this Beautiful Providence home does not disappoint Custom cabinetry in kitchen with butlers pantry lots of display cabinets Island crown moulding engineered hardwood floors in living dining kitchen area
undercabinet lighting the open concept takes your eye back to the deep conservation lot on the golf course at .26 acre it is larger and more private than other homes in the area there are 4 good sized bedrooms along with the office/den that could be a 5th bedroom suite if desired extended paver driveway leaves ample room for additional parking there is a VA mortgage that is assumable at 3.38% by a qualified buyer
